The Presidency has announced that the Channels Television will broadcast its exclusive interview with President Muhammadu Buhari on Jan. 5, 2022 at 7 p.m. The President’s spokesman, Mr Femi Adesina, made this known in a statement on Wednesday in Abuja. “Similarly, another interview session with the President by the Nigerian Television Authority (NTA) will be aired on the network service of the station on Jan. 6 at 8 p.m,” he added.